ABOUT ME

As a versatile Asian-American film director specializing in music videos, commercials, and narrative work, I draw from a diverse background in dance, choreography, animation, and music to bring a unique perspective to visual storytelling. Infusing each production with creativity and innovation, I choreograph and design everything as if it were a dance, resulting in work that is visually dynamic, seamlessly flowing, and emotionally captivating.
